Simple Control panel for my mac mini mediacenter 
Displays the status of samba shares mounted with autofs
and allows them to be remounted.

Also displays ps output for various services like:
Plex
Sabnzb+
SickBeard

Setup/Start Instructions

Change the username constant in FlaskControl.py to name of the main account
This is used to remount the shares under the right user account

Also needs to be run as root ie.

sudo python FlaskControl.py